content: Back in the concrete jungle of NYC, and the energy here is electrifying. Just saw someone walking a cat on a leash in Central Park. Only in New York!
Just turned 22. Feeling both young and old, like a paradox. Reflecting on the past year, I've grown, but it's time to push forward. New project at work, new me.
Spent the last few days diving into Python. Wrote a script that automates part of our data analysis for trading strategies. It's crude, but it's a start.
